    "name": "AbsentedAge: 亡灵少女的方格世界 International",
    "steam_appid": 1615930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span>　　</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >苏醒时，你发现自己是一位失去记忆的少女，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独自一人身处正在沉没的世界当中——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆ 这是什么样的游戏？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AbsentedAge是新式复合型游戏，非战斗时是ARPG，而在战斗中则转换为SRPG（Rougelike模式）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要接触敌人或者进行／受到先制攻击，就会无缝切换到回合制战斗模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/3a1414b58b29ddfe17fd340ce0fdf111.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/f9740341d5ebbfd4ba7d16349016db7b.poster.avif?t=1771382564\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/f9740341d5ebbfd4ba7d16349016db7b.webm?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/f9740341d5ebbfd4ba7d16349016db7b.mp4?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/8ed743690f2581c925ed0a4c3d478532.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过使用多达数百种富有战略性的技能与物品，打倒各类棘手的怪物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请熟练运用反击、精准格挡、攻击定身位移等进阶技巧，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现你独具一格、打动人心的玩法吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只要遵守使用准则，就可以自由进行本作的实况直播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/3a1414b58b29ddfe17fd340ce0fdf111.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/0c36cdba4c19e4d955a3ecef9a4e29b0.poster.avif?t=1771382564\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/0c36cdba4c19e4d955a3ecef9a4e29b0.webm?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/0c36cdba4c19e4d955a3ecef9a4e29b0.mp4?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/8ed743690f2581c925ed0a4c3d478532.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下城中的楼层移动和战斗BGM的切换都实现了无缝化，随时都有流畅无压力的快节奏游玩体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，你在游玩时所感受到的压力，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只会集中于遭遇强敌时毫无胜算的绝望，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及故事发展所带来的冲击与震撼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而这些同时也是游戏中作为主角的少女需要面对的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用智慧、勇气和善良克服它们，给自己留下最美好的回忆吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・国际版新增要素</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>英语 ←→ 原作日语的一键切换功能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏过程中，随时可通过 @ 键 / L3 按钮（可进行按键设置）<br>即时在日语与英语之间切换。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这一部分在其他语言里是怎么说的呢？”<br>“想通过游戏来进行语言学习！”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >针对这些需求，我们提供了一键即可实现的切换体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 已生成的战斗日志无法追溯并切换语言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英文翻译由 vgperson 先生负责。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是情绪饱满的精彩过场，还是道具说明中充满幽默感的文字巧思，都请尽情欣赏这份细腻而出色的翻译。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>追加街机模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全新搭载的街机模式中，玩家将在限定条件下挑战关卡攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >焕然一新的 UI 下，可体验新增的可操作角色、新技能、新装备等丰富内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及……通往下一章节的隐藏 Boss 战？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・<strong>追加可操作角色</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自《天翔のマーキナリエ》的 Allies，以及来自《リアリティ×マインズ》的 Astrake 正式参战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在街机模式中进行操作，或将其招募为同伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allies 的特点在于，能够在封锁相邻敌人行动的同时施放三段连击，具备极强的压制力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >第三段攻击会因核心更换而产生变化，因此根据战况灵活切换至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用先制攻击在命中 4 次以内不会进入战斗 的特性，刻意将连击停在第二段的战术同样十分有效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/993797ffb0bcbc71d55edc04d19d3ccd.avif?t=1771382564\" width=518 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Astrake 则与原作相同，通过技能组合可触发多样的连携追击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于追击次数多、技能配置均衡，在应对各种战局变化方面表现出色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其先制攻击分为普通技与蓄力技两种，合理区分使用将会更加有效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/52f5c598cac238d88c6be75b6ecded24.avif?t=1771382564\" width=516 height=290 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆ 瞩目点</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・可靠的搭档——塔鲁特</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以通过附魔技能组，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞬间切换与你并肩作战的精灵——塔鲁特的战斗方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >光辉附魔：虽然抗打击能力较弱，但具备飞行能力，擅长回复和支援</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/3a1414b58b29ddfe17fd340ce0fdf111.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/d04f6936192e099cfecbb6543ef942c9.poster.avif?t=1771382564\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/d04f6936192e099cfecbb6543ef942c9.webm?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/d04f6936192e099cfecbb6543ef942c9.mp4?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/8ed743690f2581c925ed0a4c3d478532.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火焰附魔：挺身而出，从正面对抗敌人，以敏捷的行动和强固的防御保护你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/3a1414b58b29ddfe17fd340ce0fdf111.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/acd451edee92ec58c89230f962837092.poster.avif?t=1771382564\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/acd451edee92ec58c89230f962837092.webm?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/acd451edee92ec58c89230f962837092.mp4?t=1771382564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/8ed743690f2581c925ed0a4c3d478532.webp?t=1771382564\" width=53 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次得到蕴藏着失落记忆的“心之碎片”时，你一定会觉醒新的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　　　――――――――――――――――――――――――――――――――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>・丰富多彩的技能、物品与换装要素</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正如上图中体现的，本作中体现在立绘上的异常状态和装备可以说非常之多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备如果过度使用就会损坏，先根据所处情况谨慎选择好装备再行动吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重复获得相同的装备，可以使装备的熟练度(+值)上升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与往年的Rougelike作品不同，提升的熟练度会在相同装备间共享，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使失去装备，熟练度也不会清零。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/cdbe6cbcd17681006467da1964197ccd.avif?t=1771382564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras_big/cdbe6cbcd17681006467da1964197ccd.avif?t=1771382564 width=800 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >相反，当再度获得因败北而丢失的装备时，熟练度还会大幅提高。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >力不能及而败北的时候，也正是取回丢失的装备并精进实力，成功雪耻的良机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　　　――――――――――――――――――――――――――――――――</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作《幽玄之章》的定位是《AbsentedAge》这一系列作品中的前篇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前篇本身已经拥有完整的剧情结构，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在本作发售时，仍存在未解禁的要素（辅助召唤、现世中的实体化行动等），以及尚未解开的神秘谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们将根据各位玩家的反馈进行本作的更新，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并同时继续进行后篇《依代之章》的开发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们随时准备好进行本作的各类改进，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论何种问题，都欢迎您通过作者推特等联系方式提供宝贵的意见。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >希望更多玩家能够来游玩本作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1615930/extras/4e141d2cbf5bd2a893981f2a87884bb2.webp?t=1771382564\" width=380 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◆ 二次创作指南 (The Guideline of derivative works)：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 本作欢迎非营利同人活动及二次创作（直播、同人创作等），</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请注意切勿构成对terunon's Lab及第三方的权力侵害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于本作的商标性质，除非另行许可，否则禁止发布以下相关内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 以本作系列官方作品名义发布的游戏作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 违反公序良俗的创作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(相关创作没有年龄限制，但请注意进行设置适当的分级)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 非官方周边商品的转让及销售</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 几乎不具备创作性，超出引用或介绍范畴的游戏内容展示</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(仅收集BGM的视频、不附带直播解说、编辑等要素的纯剧情展示视频等)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 禁止对游戏内部数据(不含游戏截图)的提取及挪用。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 发布直播视频时，请您通过标题、缩略图、视频介绍等方式注明直播内容与本作有关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 如果您是商业公司或法人组织并希望进行上述活动或创作，请联系我们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >另外，作者原则上不将以下情况视为商业活动或法人活动，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需特意咨询。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 企业Youtuber、VTuber等从事商业活动的艺人在其活动中进行本作的直播</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 通过Skeb等委托创作服务，有偿委托或创作本作的二次创作作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　- 非法人的主体通过同人志等二次创作作品获得小规模的利润</p>",
